{
    "_comment_": "VK 中央调度器配置 — 请填写 TODO 处。运行 list_organizations / list_projects / list_repos 获取 ID。",
    "organization_id": "TODO: list_organizations 获取",
    "project_id": "TODO: list_projects 获取",
